About Release:

Happy Magic: Smile Project is Aya Ueto's fifth studio album and first concept album, to be released on July 15, 2009. It will be released in two formats: limited CD+DVD+photo book edition and regular edition. "Happy Magic: Smile Project" is Ueto's first original album in over 3 years.
